Hello everyone!!


this is a django project in which we have implemented the user authentication login form and signup form

to run this project 
	$ python manage.py runserver

if django is not installed,then create a virtual enviournment and install crispy forms,django in the enviournment then run the above command


we have used to crispy forms for better user experience 
so to run this project you have install crispy forms 


	$ pip install django-crispy-forms


name of the project:intellify_project
application name: accounts


for login we have used django login view we have imported it from django.contrib.auth

for signup we have created a signup form which is present in forms.py 
we have imported itg in views.py to create a signup view


we have used static files (css) to make it look better